1
00:00:00,797 --> 00:00:04,538
Two return tickets to London, please.
两张到伦敦的往返票, 请.

2
00:00:04,992 --> 00:00:08,469
What time will the next train leave?
下一班火车什么时候开?

3
00:00:08,470 --> 00:00:11,730
At nineteen minutes past eight.
8点19分.

4
00:00:11,884 --> 00:00:13,802
Which platform?
在哪个站台?

5
00:00:14,145 --> 00:00:17,471
Platform Two. Over the bridge.
2号站台.过天桥.

6
00:00:17,472 --> 00:00:20,842
What time will the next train leave?
下一班火车什么时候开?

7
00:00:20,843 --> 00:00:23,447
At eight nineteen.
8点19分.

8
00:00:23,607 --> 00:00:26,417
We've got plenty of time.
我们的时间还很宽裕.

9
00:00:26,418 --> 00:00:29,965
It's only three minutes to eight.
现在才7点57分.

10
00:00:29,966 --> 00:00:32,924
Let's go and have a drink.
让我们去喝点东西吧,

11
00:00:33,078 --> 00:00:37,449
There's a bar next door to the station.
车站旁有一个酒吧.

12
00:00:37,590 --> 00:00:42,167
We had better go back to the station now, Ken.
Ken,我们现在最好回到车站去.

13
00:00:42,168 --> 00:00:44,624
Tickets, please.
请把车票拿出来.

14
00:00:44,754 --> 00:00:49,314
We want to catch the eight nineteen to London.
我们要乘8点19分的车去伦敦.

15
00:00:49,476 --> 00:00:52,076
You've just missed it!
你们刚好错过了那班车.

16
00:00:52,132 --> 00:00:56,583
What! It's only eight fifteen.
什么!现在只有8点15分.

17
00:00:56,584 --> 00:00:58,663
I'm sorry, sir.
对不起,先生,

18
00:00:58,664 --> 00:01:01,909
That clock's ten minutes slow.
那个钟慢了10分钟.

19
00:01:01,910 --> 00:01:04,136
When's the next train?
下一班车是什么时候?

20
00:01:04,137 --> 00:01:06,683
In five hours' time!
5个小时以后!

